      "certainty": 0.8,
      "durability": 0.55,
      "category": "persona",
      "source": "compiled",
      "tier": "short_term",
      "sourceMessageIds": []
    },
    {
      "text": "You know the photoelectric effect mattered enough for a Nobel Prize, not only relativity.",
